No. 546. Sailors’ Union of the Pacific et al., Petitioners, v. Hammond Lumber Company. January 13, 1908. Mr. Jackson H. Ralston for petitioners. Mr. S. S. Bwrdett and Mr. J. B. Thompson for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
